                        <p>Mid-sized firms (like Cordero's 50+ staff) are at AI adoption forefront (19% to 93% in one year). However, integration is a common challenge.</p>
                        <p>Only 38% of mid-sized firms use legal practice management software (vs. 71% smaller firms), suggesting potential for fragmented tech ecosystems where data is siloed.</p>
                        <p>Despite "advanced case management systems," Cordero Law likely faces integration challenges. AI with strong integration or as a unifying layer addresses a major unspoken need, enhancing value of their entire tech stack.</p>
