                            <li><strong>Leverage Mutual Connections:</strong> Warm introduction if any (community involvement, alma mater).</li>
                            <li><strong>Reference his Media Presence:</strong> Acknowledge "Consultas con Patrick Cordero" to build rapport.</li>
                            <li><strong>Initial Message Focus:</strong> Brevity, clear primary benefit, simple CTA (e.g., 15-20 min introductory call).</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

