            <section id="closing-deal" class="tab-content p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-sky-700 mb-4">VI. Closing the Deal: Moving Towards a Strategic Partnership</h2>
                <p class="mb-4 text-neutral-700">The final stage focuses on transitioning from a sales pitch to a collaborative partnership. This involves a tailored demonstration, a value-driven negotiation, and a vision for a long-term relationship, all designed to resonate with Mr. Cordero's strategic mindset.</p>

                <div class="mb-6">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-sky-600 mb-2 expandable-trigger cursor-pointer">A. Tailoring the Demo to His Firm's Specific Needs ➕</h3>
                    <div class="expandable-content ml-4 text-neutral-600 space-y-2">
                        <ul class="list-disc ml-5 space-y-1">
                            <li><strong>Focus on Relevant Use Cases:</strong> Prioritize high-volume consumer bankruptcy (60% of practice), plus real estate/family law. (e.g., AI for petition accuracy, means testing, deadline management).</li>
                            <li><strong>Highlight High-Volume Processing:</strong> Show scalability and performance under load for a 50+ staff firm.</li>
                            <li><strong>Showcase Multilingual Capabilities Prominently:</strong> English/Spanish processing, communication, translation assistance, voice-to-text.</li>
                            <li><strong>Illustrate Integration Potential:</strong> Show how it complements existing "advanced case management systems."</li>
                            <li><strong>Emphasize Ease of Use for a Large Team:</strong> Intuitive interface, easy workflows for quick adoption.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="mb-6">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-sky-600 mb-2 expandable-trigger cursor-pointer">B. Negotiation Strategy: Highlighting Long-Term Value ➕</h3>
                    <div class="expandable-content ml-4 text-neutral-600 space-y-2">
                        <ul class="list-disc ml-5 space-y-1">
                            <li><strong>Frame as a Strategic Investment:</strong> Focus on sustainable ROI, enhanced profitability (appeals to finance background).</li>
                            <li><strong>Emphasize Scalability and Future-Proofing:</strong> Aligns with "never stop improving" and "intersection of tradition and innovation."</li>
                            <li><strong>Discuss Partnership Benefits:</strong> Early access to new features, co-development opportunities, joint thought leadership.</li>
                            <li><strong>Flexible and Phased Options:</strong> Implementation/subscription models suiting capacity/budget, pilot program.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
